defaulte now academies. An
defaultd b
defaultecoming an academy has helped some schools to 
defaultmake 
defaultsignificant improvement
defaults
default. But by no means
default all academies have been successful, nor have all the successful maintained schools 
defaultchosen to become academies. The picture is very complex, and 
defaultvery different 
defaulti
defaultn different parts of the country
default.
